================ *** Map ***  ====================

1.  => npx expo-cli install react-native-maps {pre-installed when Project generated with expo-cli}
2.  => npx expo-cli install expo-location {it access the user location by asking from user via OS}


  const startWatching = async () => {
    try {
      const { granted } = await requestPermissionsAsync();
      if (!granted) {
        throw new Error('Location permission not granted');
      }
    } catch (e) {
      setErr(e);
    }
  };

  abd shell pm reset-permissions
